"description":"Great Music, it said, and Great Poetry would like quieten Modern Youth down and make Modern Youth more Civilized. Civilized my syphilised yarbles.<br /><br />\nIn Anthony Burgess's influential nightmare vision of the future, criminals take over after dark. Teen gang leader Alex narrates in fantastically inventive slang that echoes the violent intensity of youth rebelling against society. Dazzling and transgressive, A Clockwork Orange is a frightening fable about good and evil and the meaning of human freedom.", "formattedPrice":"$0.99", "trackCensoredName":"A Clockwork Orange", "artistViewUrl":"https://books.apple.com/us/artist/anthony-burgess/46814361?uo=4", "trackViewUrl":"https://books.apple.com/us/book/a-clockwork-orange/id1519750509?uo=4",
